title: SPY Surf Commercial hits FUEL TV
description:
You know that dream you had where a post-surf Alana Blanchard was walking in slow-motion and Wade Goodall was punting airs all over the place? Wake up sleepy head, it's here courtesy of your friends at SPY.

Check out the pre-surf amp commercial on the big screen airing now on Fuel TV.
